/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b140db34a8e28bd57fa355e20364086cc2b0bd0","tid":164650,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而我擔心台灣買左THAAD之後，D技術俾支那間諜偷哂就好笑</blockquote><br />\n一定會，依加國軍嘅腐化程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美軍應該唔會on9 到咁...一係佢地派人自己睇返 收月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n參考番台灣座樂山美軍基地，直情唔比任何人行近"}]}